thread.title: INSIGHT: Abu Dhabi's sky comes to life in air race

title: INSIGHT: Abu Dhabi's sky comes to life in air race
text:
INSIGHT: Abu Dhabi's sky comes to life in air race 1:26pm EST - 00:43 
American pilot Michael Goulian took his first Red Bull air race victory in nine years on Saturday when he defeated Yoshihide Muroya and Kirby Chambliss in Abu Dhabi. His last victory was in Budapest in 2009 but had set the pace all week leading up to the race.
